criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  above 18 years of age;

          -  diagnosis of grade 2 or 3 endometrial cancer, or high grade type (serous or clear
             cell), stage 1b1 or stage 2a cervical cancer, stage 1 vulvar cancer with tumor greater
             than 4 cm, or stage 2 or 3 vulvar cancer;

          -  to undergo surgical lymph node dissection.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  recurrent diagnosis of gynecological cancer;

          -  presence of distant metastases (stage 4 cancer);

          -  body mass index of 35 or greater.
